<Layout title="Privacy Policy - StepDebt">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>
    StepDebt respects your privacy. This app does not collect, store, or share
    any personal data with third parties.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      All data (such as step counts, goals, bank, and debt) is stored locally on
      your device.
    </li>
    <li>The app does not transmit any information to external servers.</li>
    <li>We do not use analytics, ads, or tracking of any kind.</li>
    <li>
      You are fully in control of your data. Deleting the app will permanently
      remove all stored information.
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    If you have any questions about privacy, feel free to contact us at:
    <a href="mailto:info@stepdebt.com">info@stepdebt.com</a>
  </p>
</Layout>
